.80.ec.88.98","title":"매개변수","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>텍스트</code> 생성된 텍스트 노드입니다.</li>\n <li><code>데이터</code> 텍스트 노드에 쓰여지는 문자열입니다.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ec.98.88.ec.a0.9c","title":"예제","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;html&gt;\n&lt;head&gt;\n&lt;title&gt;createTextNode 예제&lt;/title&gt;\n\n&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;\n\nfunction addTextNode()\n{\nvar newtext = document.createTextNode(\" 동적으로 추가되는 텍스트. \");\nvar para = document.getElementById(\"p1\");\npara.appendChild(newtext);\n}\n\n&lt;/script&gt;\n&lt;/head&gt;\n\n&lt;body&gt;\n&lt;div style=\"border: 1px solid red\"&gt;\n&lt;p id=\"p1\"&gt;단락의 첫번째 줄.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\n\n&lt;button onclick=\"addTextNode();\"&gt;TextNode 추가하기.&lt;/button&gt;\n\n&lt;/body&gt;\n&lt;/html&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":".ea.b7.9c.ec.95.bd","title":"규약","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Core-20001113/core.html#ID-1975348127\" rel=\" noopener\">createTextNode </a></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"텍스트 노드를 생성합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Document.createTextNode()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Document.createTextNode()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Document.createTextNode()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"document.createTextNode","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Document.createTextNode()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"document.createTextNode","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Document.createTextNode()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Document.createTextNode()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Document.createTextNode()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/document/createtextnode","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/documen